Portions derived from semble

semeja reimplements ideas from semble (https://github.com/MinishLab/semble),
Copyright (c) 2026 Thomas van Dongen, MIT License. Copyright does not protect
ideas or algorithms, so semeja's independent reimplementation of semble's
design is original work owned by the semeja authors.

The following files, however, contain data tables, regular expressions, or
text copied or closely adapted from semble. Those specific portions remain
Copyright (c) 2026 Thomas van Dongen and are used here under semble's MIT
License (terms above):

  - src/lang_table.rs        file-extension and documentation-language tables
  - src/rank/boost.rs        symbol-query / embedded-symbol regexes, keyword
                             and stopword lists
  - src/rank/penalty.rs      test-file and path-pattern regexes
  - agents/semeja-search.md  agent definition text
  - tests/                   test cases ported from semble's test suite
